data.description: Come see this quaint ranch style home with NO HOA and conveniently located near Charleston AFB, Boeing, Bosch and I-26! This 3 bed / 2 bath home is situated on a quiet fenced in lot with mature trees with a great backyard for relaxing or entertaining. Inside, you will see beautiful vinyl floors throughout the home as well as granite countertops and a beautiful tiled backsplash in the kitchen! The master bedroom has its own en-suite bathroom and large closet. The two spares are spacious enough for guests or children and share their own full bath. Come take a look at this meticulously kept home before its gone!
